{"tha-ap366:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap366:0.2":"Mandaravapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap366:0.3":"Kesarapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap366:1.1":"“Vijjadharo tada asim, ","tha-ap366:1.2":"himavantamhi pabbate; ","tha-ap366:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap366:1.4":"cankamantam mahayasam. ","tha-ap366:2.1":"Tini kesarapupphani, ","tha-ap366:2.2":"sise katvanaham tada; ","tha-ap366:2.3":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap366:2.4":"vessabhum abhipujayim. ","tha-ap366:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap366:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap366:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap366:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap366:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap366:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap366:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap366:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kesarapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap366:6.1":"Kesarapupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}